               stealing, on the <rs id="t18260406-322-cd1723" type="crimeDate">6th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260406-322-off1722 t18260406-322-cd1723"></join>, 1 wooden chest, value 2s. 6d., and 50lbs. weight of tea, value 13l. 15s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t18260406-322-victim1718" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Conway
               <interp inst="t18260406-322-victim1718" type="surname" value="Conway"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260406-322-victim1718" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
